screen_desc: The screenshot shows a screen from the Uber app asking the user to accept Uber's Terms of Use and review the Privacy Notice. The user is informed that by selecting "I Agree" below, they confirm they have reviewed and agree to the Terms of Use and acknowledge the Privacy Notice, and that they are at least 18 years of age. There are two buttons at the bottom: a back arrow on the left and a "Next" button on the right.
